<div id="outline-container-orga25d2d6" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orga25d2d6"><span class="section-number-2">1</span> 三公</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org53d7ffa" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org53d7ffa"><span class="section-number-3">1.1</span> 相国、丞相（大司徒）</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-1">
<p>
秦官​金印紫绶，掌丞天子助理万机。​有两长史，秩千石​秦有左右，高帝即位，置一丞相，十一年更名相国，绿绶。孝惠、高后置左右丞相，文帝二年复置一丞相。​哀帝元寿二年更名大司徒。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org335c7f2" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org335c7f2"><span class="section-number-3">1.2</span> 太尉（大司马、将军）</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-2">
<p>
秦官​金印紫授，掌武事。​有长史，秩千石。​武帝建元二年省。元狩四年初置大司马，以冠将军之号，宣帝地节三年置大司马，不冠将军，亦元印绶官属。成帝绥和元年初赐在司马金印紫绶，置官属，禄比丞相，去将军。哀帝建平二年复去大司马印绶、官属，冠将军如故。元寿二年复赐大司马印绶，置官属，去将军，位在司徒上。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org15412ae" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org15412ae"><span class="section-number-3">1.3</span> 御史大夫（大司空、御史中丞）</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-3">
<p>
秦官​位上卿，银印青绶，掌副丞相。一曰中丞，在殿中兰台，掌图籍秘书，外督部刺史，内领侍御史员十五人，受公卿奏事，举劾按章。​有两丞，秩千石。​成帝绶和元年更名大司空，金印紫绶，禄比丞相，置长史如中丞，官职如故。哀帝建平二年复为御史大夫，元寿二年复为大司空，御史中丞更名御史长史。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgc3c3fdc" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgc3c3fdc"><span class="section-number-3">1.4</span> 太傅、太师、太保（古官三公）</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-4">
<p>
古官​金印紫绶。​太傅，高后元年初置。后省，八年复置。哀帝元寿二年复置。位在三公上。太师、太保，平帝元始元年皆初置。太师位在太傅上，太保次太傅。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgbff7d2a" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgbff7d2a"><span class="section-number-2">2</span> 九卿</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-2">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org97a8d6c" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org97a8d6c"><span class="section-number-3">2.1</span> 奉常（太常、秩宗）</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-2-1">
<p>
秦官​掌宗庙礼仪，有丞。​景帝中六年更名太常。王莽改太常曰秩宗。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org191ce19" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org191ce19"><span class="section-number-4">2.1.1</span> 六令丞</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-1-1">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>太乐</li>
</ul>
<p>
掌伎乐
</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>太祝</li>
</ul>
<p>
掌祭祀​景帝中六年更名太祝为祠祀，武帝太初元年更曰庙祀，初置太卜。
</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>太宰</li>
</ul>
<p>
掌膳食
</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>太史</li>
</ul>
<p>
掌天时星历
</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>太卜</li>
</ul>
<p>
掌占卜
</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>太医</li>
</ul>
<p>
掌医药
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org7e6e347" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org7e6e347"><span class="section-number-4">2.1.2</span> 两长丞</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-1-2">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1a77a91" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org1a77a91"><span class="section-number-5">2.1.2.1</span> 都水</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-1-2-1">
<p>
总掌治水
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgba36f41" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgba36f41"><span class="section-number-5">2.1.2.2</span> 均官</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-1-2-2">
<p>
掌均输
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org484fcc3" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org484fcc3"><span class="section-number-4">2.1.3</span> 诸庙寝园食官令长丞</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgdd49b2f" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgdd49b2f"><span class="section-number-4">2.1.4</span> 雍五畤相关</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-1-4">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org69c6a46" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org69c6a46"><span class="section-number-5">2.1.4.1</span> 雍太宰</h5>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org4d62eb2" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org4d62eb2"><span class="section-number-5">2.1.4.2</span> 雍太祝</h5>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1bdaac6" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org1bdaac6"><span class="section-number-5">2.1.4.3</span> 五畤尉</h5>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org9a1a9e8" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org9a1a9e8"><span class="section-number-4">2.1.5</span> 博士</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-1-5">
<p>
秦官​博古通今，备顾问，传授儒学。​​秩比六百石，员多至数十人。武帝建元五年初置《五经》博士，宣帝黄龙元年稍增员十二人。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org75525c1" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org75525c1"><span class="section-number-4">2.1.6</span> 诸陵县</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-1-6">
<p>
掌陵寝诸事​元帝永光元年分诸陵邑属三辅。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org5985f70" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org5985f70"><span class="section-number-3">2.2</span> 郎中令（光禄勋）</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-2-2">
<p>
秦官​掌宫殿掖门户，有丞。​武帝太初元年更名光禄勋。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org8b4f242" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org8b4f242"><span class="section-number-4">2.2.1</span> 大夫</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-2-1">
<p>
掌论议，有太中大夫、中大夫、谏大夫，皆无员，多至数十人。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org42ca34c" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org42ca34c"><span class="section-number-5">2.2.1.1</span> 太中大夫</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-2-1-1">
<p>
太中大夫秩比千石
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgfa0049b" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgfa0049b"><span class="section-number-5">2.2.1.2</span> 中大夫</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-2-1-2">
<p>
太初元年更名中大夫为光禄大夫，秩比二千石
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org959474e" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org959474e"><span class="section-number-5">2.2.1.3</span> 谏大夫</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-2-1-3">
<p>
武帝元狩五年初置谏大夫，秩比八百石
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org4476c17" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org4476c17"><span class="section-number-4">2.2.2</span> 郎</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-2-2">
<p>
掌守门户，出充车骑，有议郎、中郎、侍郎、郎中，皆无员，多至千人。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orga7b4dc0" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orga7b4dc0"><span class="section-number-5">2.2.2.1</span> 议郎</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-2-2-1">
<p>
秩比六百石
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgdf2bb73" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgdf2bb73"><span class="section-number-5">2.2.2.2</span> 中郎</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-2-2-2">
<p>
秩比六百石
</p>
</div>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="org2fbee5c"></a>五官、左、右三将<br />
<div class="outline-text-6" id="text-2-2-2-2-1">
<p>
秩皆比二千石
</p>
</div>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgf44d1ee" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgf44d1ee"><span class="section-number-5">2.2.2.3</span> 侍郎</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-2-2-3">
<p>
秩比四百石
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org2a6fc4d" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org2a6fc4d"><span class="section-number-5">2.2.2.4</span> 郎中</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-2-2-4">
<p>
秩比三百石
</p>
</div>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="orge3aae80"></a>车、户、骑三将<br />
<div class="outline-text-6" id="text-2-2-2-4-1">
<p>
秩皆比千石
</p>
</div>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgb20e0e5" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgb20e0e5"><span class="section-number-4">2.2.3</span> 谒者</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-2-3">
<p>
掌宾讚受事​员七十人，秩比六百石
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org92c69e1" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org92c69e1"><span class="section-number-5">2.2.3.1</span> 谒者仆射</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-2-3-1">
<p>
秩比千石
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org51e9e19" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org51e9e19"><span class="section-number-4">2.2.4</span> 期门（虎贲郎）</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-2-4">
<p>
掌执兵送从。​比郎，无员，多至千人。武帝建元三年初置，平帝元始元年更名虎贲郎。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org9efb0bd" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org9efb0bd"><span class="section-number-5">2.2.4.1</span> 期门仆射</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-2-4-1">
<p>
秩比千石
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org8cf6321" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org8cf6321"><span class="section-number-5">2.2.4.2</span> 虎贲中郎将</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-2-4-2">
<p>
秩比二千石
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgc22c694" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgc22c694"><span class="section-number-4">2.2.5</span> 羽林</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-2-5">
<p>
掌送从，次期门。​羽林有令丞。​武帝太初元年初置，名曰建章营骑，后更名羽林骑。又取从军死事之子孙养羽林，官教以五兵，号曰羽林孤儿。宣帝令中郎将、骑都尉监羽林，秩比二千石。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org6f321c3" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org6f321c3"><span class="section-number-3">2.3</span> 卫尉（中大夫令）</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-2-3">
<p>
秦官​掌宫门卫屯兵，有丞。​景帝初更名中大夫令，后元年复为卫尉。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orga6000e3" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orga6000e3"><span class="section-number-4">2.3.1</span> 公车司马</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org4b3078d" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org4b3078d"><span class="section-number-4">2.3.2</span> 卫士</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgfa6b768" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgfa6b768"><span class="section-number-4">2.3.3</span> 旅贲</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orge5aa596" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orge5aa596"><span class="section-number-4">2.3.4</span> 诸屯卫候</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org643cb80" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org643cb80"><span class="section-number-4">2.3.5</span> 司马二十二官</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org021309b" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org021309b"><span class="section-number-4">2.3.6</span> 长乐卫尉</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org87e0e49" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org87e0e49"><span class="section-number-4">2.3.7</span> 建章卫尉</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org18d2516" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org18d2516"><span class="section-number-4">2.3.8</span> 甘泉卫尉</h4>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org29f963b" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org29f963b"><span class="section-number-3">2.4</span> 太仆</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-2-4">
<p>
秦官​掌舆马，有两丞。​​秩中二千石。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org402f37e" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org402f37e"><span class="section-number-4">2.4.1</span> 太厩</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-4-1">
<p>
五丞一尉
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orge347a2a" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orge347a2a"><span class="section-number-4">2.4.2</span> 未央</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-4-2">
<p>
五丞一尉​未央厩令
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1caab99" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org1caab99"><span class="section-number-4">2.4.3</span> 家马（挏马）</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-4-3">
<p>
五丞一尉​主供天子私用，非大祀戎事军国所需，故谓之家马也。​武帝太初元年更名家马为挏马，初置路。
四令丞
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org2fa6ae5" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org2fa6ae5"><span class="section-number-5">2.4.3.1</span> 车府</h5>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org5807869" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org5807869"><span class="section-number-5">2.4.3.2</span> 路</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-4-3-2">
<p>
厩名​，在未央宫。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org5e5f8e6" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org5e5f8e6"><span class="section-number-5">2.4.3.3</span> 骑马</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-4-3-3">
<p>
厩名​，在长安城外。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org23ab61c" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org23ab61c"><span class="section-number-5">2.4.3.4</span> 骏马</h5>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgcd88fe1" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgcd88fe1"><span class="section-number-4">2.4.4</span> 五监长丞</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-4-4">
<p>
龙马、闲驹、橐泉、騊駼、承华龙马，大宛厩也。闲驹，养马之所​。橐泉，厩名，在橐泉宫下。騊駼，厩名，在长安城外。承华，厩名。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org9618c90" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org9618c90"><span class="section-number-4">2.4.5</span> 边郡六牧师苑令</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-4-5">
<p>
陇西、天水、安定、北地、上郡、西河六郡
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgc3f63b4" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgc3f63b4"><span class="section-number-4">2.4.6</span> 牧橐令丞</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-4-6">
<p>
牧养骆驼
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org0ca6a12" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org0ca6a12"><span class="section-number-4">2.4.7</span> 昆蹄令丞</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-4-7">
<p>
良马厩
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgb597b4c" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgb597b4c"><span class="section-number-4">2.4.8</span> 中太仆</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-4-8">
<p>
掌皇太后舆马，不常置也。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgf79523a" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgf79523a"><span class="section-number-3">2.5</span> 廷尉（大理、作士）</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-2-5">
<p>
秦官​掌刑辟。​​秩中二千石。​有正、左右监，秩皆千石。​景帝中六年更名大理，武帝建元四年复为廷尉。宣帝地节三年初置左右平，秩皆六百石。帝元寿二年复为大理。王莽改曰作士。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1a08efa" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org1a08efa"><span class="section-number-3">2.6</span> 典客（大行令、大鸿胪、典乐）</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-2-6">
<p>
秦官​掌诸归义蛮夷，有丞。​​秩中二千石。​景帝中六年更名大行令，武帝太初元年更名大鸿胪。王莽改大鸿胪曰典乐。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org903b5d4" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org903b5d4"><span class="section-number-4">2.6.1</span> 行人</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-6-1">
<p>
武帝太初元年更名行人为大行令
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org09852d3" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org09852d3"><span class="section-number-4">2.6.2</span> 译官</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgedce4d8" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgedce4d8"><span class="section-number-4">2.6.3</span> 别火</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-6-3">
<p>
狱令，主治改火之事。​武帝太初元年，初置别火。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org40a47e4" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org40a47e4"><span class="section-number-4">2.6.4</span> 郡邸长丞</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-6-4">
<p>
诸郡在京师之邸，郡国朝宿之舍。​初，置郡国邸属少府，中属中尉，后属大鸿胪。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org94721c2" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org94721c2"><span class="section-number-3">2.7</span> 宗正</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-2-7">
<p>
秦官​掌亲属，有丞。​​秩中二千石。​平帝元始四年更名宗伯。​王莽并其官于秩宗。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org7921e4f" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org7921e4f"><span class="section-number-4">2.7.1</span> 都司空令丞</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-7-1">
<p>
都造砖瓦，用以修葺宫殿及各城门楼
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org8e78158" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org8e78158"><span class="section-number-4">2.7.2</span> 内官长丞</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-7-2">
<p>
初，内官属少府，中属主爵，后属宗正。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgfb40001" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgfb40001"><span class="section-number-4">2.7.3</span> 公主家令</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgb9e0a6a" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgb9e0a6a"><span class="section-number-4">2.7.4</span> 公主门尉</h4>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org43286e5" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org43286e5"><span class="section-number-3">2.8</span> 治粟内史（大农令、大司农）</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-2-8">
<p>
秦官。​掌谷货，有两丞。​​秩中二千石。​景帝后元年更名大农令，武帝太初元年更名大司农。王莽改大司农曰羲和，后更为纳言。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgfaf5e11" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgfaf5e11"><span class="section-number-4">2.8.1</span> 五令丞</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-8-1">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgffab769" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgffab769"><span class="section-number-5">2.8.1.1</span> 太仓</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-8-1-1">
<p>
京城储粮大仓
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1a498e9" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org1a498e9"><span class="section-number-5">2.8.1.2</span> 均输</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-8-1-2">
<p>
统一征收，买卖和运输货物，以调剂各地需求，郡国设均输官。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org21e7b2e" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org21e7b2e"><span class="section-number-5">2.8.1.3</span> 平准</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-8-1-3">
<p>
官府转输物资，平抑物价，由平准令掌管。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org4db4bf1" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org4db4bf1"><span class="section-number-5">2.8.1.4</span> 都内</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-8-1-4">
<p>
主管贡献方物及货币
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org686bcb3" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org686bcb3"><span class="section-number-5">2.8.1.5</span> 籍田</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-8-1-5">
<p>
初为帝王亲耕，并设仓，后因仓设官。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org91e567d" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org91e567d"><span class="section-number-4">2.8.2</span> 两长丞</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-8-2">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org7f351c6" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org7f351c6"><span class="section-number-5">2.8.2.1</span> 干官</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-8-2-1">
<p>
掌铸钱事。​初，斡官属少府，中属主爵，后属大司农。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org2890aa1" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org2890aa1"><span class="section-number-5">2.8.2.2</span> 铁市</h5>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgd2df96c" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgd2df96c"><span class="section-number-4">2.8.3</span> 郡国诸仓</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org533a043" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org533a043"><span class="section-number-4">2.8.4</span> 农监</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org01b5080" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org01b5080"><span class="section-number-4">2.8.5</span> 都水六十五官长丞</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org7b80046" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org7b80046"><span class="section-number-4">2.8.6</span> 搜粟都尉</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-8-6">
<p>
武帝军官，不常置。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1067bd2" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org1067bd2"><span class="section-number-3">2.9</span> 少府</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-2-9">
<p>
秦官​掌山海池泽之税，以给供养，有六丞。​​秩中二千石。​王莽改少府曰共工。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org21e8409" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org21e8409"><span class="section-number-4">2.9.1</span> 十六官令丞</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-9-1">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgd727460" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgd727460"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.1</span> 尚书</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-1">
<p>
初掌殿内文书，后掌群臣章奏。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org6298c76" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org6298c76"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.2</span> 符节</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-2">
<p>
掌符节之事。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orga68d3e7" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orga68d3e7"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.3</span> 太医</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-3">
<p>
主治宫廷人员之病。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgd74f6b1" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgd74f6b1"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.4</span> 太官</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-4">
<p>
掌膳食，兼掌四时进献果实。​太官七丞。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1109722" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org1109722"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.5</span> 汤官</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-5">
<p>
供饼饵果实。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org4bc6857" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org4bc6857"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.6</span> 导官</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-6">
<p>
掌御用粮食。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org4bd6588" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org4bd6588"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.7</span> 乐府</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-7">
<p>
主管宫廷、巡行、祭祀之音乐，兼采民歌及配曲。​乐府三丞。​绥和二年，哀帝省乐府。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orga3349ad" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orga3349ad"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.8</span> 若庐</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-8">
<p>
主治库兵及诏狱。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgd443e7c" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgd443e7c"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.9</span> 考工室</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-9">
<p>
主作兵器弓弩及织绶诸杂工。​武帝太初元年更名考工室为考工。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org9df40e0" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org9df40e0"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.10</span> 左弋</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-10">
<p>
掌助弋射之事，兼造兵器。​武帝太初元年更名左弋为飞（次蜚）。​飞掌弋射，有九丞两尉。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orge389652" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orge389652"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.11</span> 居室</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-11">
<p>
拘禁犯人之所。​武帝太初元年更名居室为保宫
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org39bdd6e" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org39bdd6e"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.12</span> 甘泉居室</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-12">
<p>
武帝太初元年更名为昆台。​昆台五丞。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org9cbca2f" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org9cbca2f"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.13</span> 左右司空</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-13">
<p>
主造陶瓦，兼石刻工艺。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org22c1aea" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org22c1aea"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.14</span> 东织</h5>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgc2fdd62" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgc2fdd62"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.15</span> 西织</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-15">
<p>
掌皇家丝帛织造，在未央宫。​河平元年省东织，更名西织为织室。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1cdfc91" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org1cdfc91"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.1.16</span> 东园匠</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-1-16">
<p>
掌陵墓内器物制作和供应。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org6d86ee6" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org6d86ee6"><span class="section-number-4">2.9.2</span> 三长丞</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-9-2">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgbb510db" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgbb510db"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.2.1</span> 庖人</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-2-1">
<p>
掌宰割者。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org982430d" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org982430d"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.2.2</span> 都水</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-2-2">
<p>
掌陂泽。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1bdcf20" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org1bdcf20"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.2.3</span> 均官</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-2-3">
<p>
掌少府均输事。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgebe6e0e" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgebe6e0e"><span class="section-number-4">2.9.3</span> 上林中十池监</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org824ca5c" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org824ca5c"><span class="section-number-4">2.9.4</span> 八官食丞</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-9-4">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgfaf3d24" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgfaf3d24"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.4.1</span> 中书谒者令</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-4-1">
<p>
掌机要，由宦者充任。​成帝建始四年更名中书谒者令为中谒者令，初置尚书，员五人，有四丞。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org09be6ac" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org09be6ac"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.4.2</span> 黄门令</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-4-2">
<p>
主省中诸宦者
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org40ad1e6" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org40ad1e6"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.4.3</span> 鉤盾令</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-4-3">
<p>
宦者典诸近池苑囿游观之处。​钩盾五丞两尉
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org16a9fd4" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org16a9fd4"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.4.4</span> 尚方令</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-4-4">
<p>
掌管供应制造帝王所用器物。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgc95efd9" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgc95efd9"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.4.5</span> 御府令</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-4-5">
<p>
宦者典宫婢作中衣服及补浣之属。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org92e703d" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org92e703d"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.4.6</span> 永巷令</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-4-6">
<p>
宦者典宫婢侍使。​武帝太初元年更名永巷为掖庭。​掖廷八丞。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org3f1e457" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org3f1e457"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.4.7</span> 内者令</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-4-7">
<p>
掌客庭布张诸衣物。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orga0dec86" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orga0dec86"><span class="section-number-5">2.9.4.8</span> 宦者令</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-2-9-4-8">
<p>
管内廷宦者。​宦者七丞。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org46778f7" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org46778f7"><span class="section-number-4">2.9.5</span> 仆射</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-9-5">
<p>
首长之义。秦汉时凡侍中、尚书、博士、谒者、郎等官，都有仆射。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org02253ff" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org02253ff"><span class="section-number-4">2.9.6</span> 署长</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org552e431" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org552e431"><span class="section-number-4">2.9.7</span> 中黄门</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-9-7">
<p>
宦者掌给事中
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org312bc1b" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org312bc1b"><span class="section-number-2">3</span> 中尉（执金吾）</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-3">
<p>
秦官​掌徼循京师。​秩中二千石。​有两丞、候、司马、千人。​武帝太初元年更名执金吾。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org6a1497e" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org6a1497e"><span class="section-number-3">3.1</span> 四令丞</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-3-1">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org9964de0" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org9964de0"><span class="section-number-4">3.1.1</span> 中垒</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-3-1-1">
<p>
​两尉
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgcb99b92" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgcb99b92"><span class="section-number-4">3.1.2</span> 寺互</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-3-1-2">
<p>
初，寺互属少府，中属主爵，后属中尉。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org701f56e" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org701f56e"><span class="section-number-4">3.1.3</span> 武库</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-3-1-3">
<p>
三丞
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org472224d" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org472224d"><span class="section-number-4">3.1.4</span> 都船</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-3-1-4">
<p>
主船之官。​三丞
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1090f3c" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org1090f3c"><span class="section-number-3">3.2</span> 式道左右中侯</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-3-2">
<p>
凡左、右、中三侯车驾出，掌在前清道。车驾还，持麾至宫门，门乃开。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orge59eaf9" class="outline-3">
