<div id="outline-container-org6af49fc" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org6af49fc"><span class="section-number-3">4.8</span> 舍人</h3>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org0fe60c7" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org0fe60c7"><span class="section-number-2">5</span> 将作少府（将作大匠）</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-5">
<p>
秦官​掌治宫室。​有两丞、左右中候。​景帝中六年更名将作大匠。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org7a09b7d" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org7a09b7d"><span class="section-number-3">5.1</span> 七令丞</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-5-1">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orge7bebb0" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orge7bebb0"><span class="section-number-4">5.1.1</span> 石库</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org545edd0" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org545edd0"><span class="section-number-4">5.1.2</span> 东园主章</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-5-1-2">
<p>
掌大材，以供东园大匠。​武帝太初元年更名东园主章为木工。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org416850a" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org416850a"><span class="section-number-4">5.1.3</span> 左右前后中校</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-5-1-3">
<p>
成帝阳朔三年省中候及左右前后中校五丞。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org43fc18b" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org43fc18b"><span class="section-number-3">5.2</span> 主章长丞</h3>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orge1b698c" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orge1b698c"><span class="section-number-2">6</span> 詹事</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-6">
<p>
秦官。​掌皇后、太子家，有丞。​成帝鸿嘉三年省詹事官，并属大长秋。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org484509b" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org484509b"><span class="section-number-3">6.1</span> 太子率更</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-6-1">
<p>
掌知漏刻，秩千石。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org22977a9" class="outline-3">
