<div id="outline-container-org5964511" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org5964511"><span class="section-number-2">10</span> 三辅</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-10">
<p>
元鼎四年更置三辅都尉、都尉丞各一人。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgb3c3e08" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgb3c3e08"><span class="section-number-3">10.1</span> 内史</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-10-1">
<p>
周官，秦因之。​掌治京师。​景帝二年分置左右内史。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org728ee4e" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org728ee4e"><span class="section-number-4">10.1.1</span> 左内史（左冯翊）</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-10-1-1">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org24b8ff4" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org24b8ff4"><span class="section-number-5">10.1.1.1</span> 廪栖令丞尉</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-10-1-1-1">
<p>
掌祭祀牺牲之属。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org2878e9a" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org2878e9a"><span class="section-number-5">10.1.1.2</span> 左都水</h5>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgee9b7bd" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgee9b7bd"><span class="section-number-5">10.1.1.3</span> 铁官</h5>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orged7de25" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orged7de25"><span class="section-number-5">10.1.1.4</span> 云垒</h5>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org26e1fb1" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org26e1fb1"><span class="section-number-5">10.1.1.5</span> 长安四市四长丞</h5>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org46089ec" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org46089ec"><span class="section-number-4">10.1.2</span> 右内史（京兆尹）</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-10-1-2">
<p>
右内史武帝太初元年更名京兆尹。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgbacf834" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgbacf834"><span class="section-number-5">10.1.2.1</span> 两令丞</h5>
