<li><a id="org9386d92"></a>长安令丞<br /></li>
<li><a id="orge3be41b"></a>厨令丞<br />
<div class="outline-text-6" id="text-10-1-2-1-2">
<p>
掌帝王巡幸境内离宫别馆时之供帐。
</p>
</div>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org04c53ed" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org04c53ed"><span class="section-number-5">10.1.2.2</span> 两长丞</h5>
