<div id="outline-container-org98d7942" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org98d7942"><span class="section-number-3">10.2</span> 主爵中尉（都尉、右扶风）</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-10-2">
<p>
秦官。​掌列侯。​景帝中六年更名都尉，武帝太初元年更名右扶风。治内史右地。列侯更属大鸿胪。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org8cae034" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org8cae034"><span class="section-number-4">10.2.1</span> 掌畜令丞</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org4318f58" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org4318f58"><span class="section-number-4">10.2.2</span> 四长丞</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-10-2-2">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orga92f013" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orga92f013"><span class="section-number-5">10.2.2.1</span> 右都水</h5>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org9a4594c" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org9a4594c"><span class="section-number-5">10.2.2.2</span> 铁官</h5>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org594c38b" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org594c38b"><span class="section-number-5">10.2.2.3</span> 厩</h5>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgdc0f366" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgdc0f366"><span class="section-number-5">10.2.2.4</span> 雍厨</h5>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org63ecdb2" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org63ecdb2"><span class="section-number-2">11</span> 武职</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-11">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgce0a3fa" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgce0a3fa"><span class="section-number-3">11.1</span> 前后左右将军</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-11-1">
<p>
周末官，秦因之。​金印紫绶。皆掌兵及四夷。​有长史，秩千石。​皆周末官，秦因之，位上卿。汉不常置。或有前后，或有左右。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgfb5d386" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgfb5d386"><span class="section-number-3">11.2</span> 护军都尉（司寇）</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-11-2">
<p>
秦官。​武帝元狩四年属大司马，成帝绥和元年居大司马府比司直，哀帝元寿元年更名司寇，平帝元始元年更名护军。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org6bdaf0a" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org6bdaf0a"><span class="section-number-3">11.3</span> 司隶校尉</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-11-3">
<p>
周官。​武帝征和四年初置。持节，从中都官徒千二百人，捕巫蛊，督大奸猾。后罢其兵，察三辅、三河、弘农。元帝初元四年去节，成帝元延四年省。绥和二年，哀帝复置，但为司隶，属大司空，比司直。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org55242f2" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org55242f2"><span class="section-number-3">11.4</span> 城门校尉</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-11-4">
<p>
掌京师城门屯兵。​有司马、十二城门候。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgdef1cdf" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgdef1cdf"><span class="section-number-3">11.5</span> 八校尉</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-11-5">
<p>
武帝初置，有丞、司马。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org929e779" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org929e779"><span class="section-number-4">11.5.1</span> 中垒校尉</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-11-5-1">
<p>
掌北军垒门内，外掌西域。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgef9ebf2" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgef9ebf2"><span class="section-number-4">11.5.2</span> 屯骑校尉</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-11-5-2">
<p>
掌骑士。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org2c0dadc" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org2c0dadc"><span class="section-number-4">11.5.3</span> 步兵校尉</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-11-5-3">
<p>
掌上林苑门屯兵。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orge4180e8" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orge4180e8"><span class="section-number-4">11.5.4</span> 越骑校尉越骑。</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org76998e3" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org76998e3"><span class="section-number-4">11.5.5</span> 长水校尉</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-11-5-5">
<p>
掌长水宣曲胡骑。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgface564" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgface564"><span class="section-number-4">11.5.6</span> 胡骑校尉</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-11-5-6">
<p>
掌池阳胡骑，不常置。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org0093ac4" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org0093ac4"><span class="section-number-4">11.5.7</span> 射声校尉</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-11-5-7">
<p>
掌待诏射声士。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org46877ed" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org46877ed"><span class="section-number-4">11.5.8</span> 虎贲校尉</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-11-5-8">
<p>
掌轻车。​
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org2f1ef38" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org2f1ef38"><span class="section-number-3">11.6</span> 西域都护加官</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-11-6">
<p>
宣帝地节二年初置，以骑都尉、谏大夫使护西域三十六国，有副校尉，秩比二千石，丞一人，司马、侯、千人各二人。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgbde443f" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgbde443f"><span class="section-number-3">11.7</span> 戊已校尉</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-11-7">
<p>
掌西域屯田事务。​元帝初元元年置，有丞、司马各一人，侯五人，秩比六百石。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org20227aa" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org20227aa"><span class="section-number-3">11.8</span> 奉车都尉</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-11-8">
<p>
掌御乘舆车。​武帝初置，秩比二千石。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1dafdae" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org1dafdae"><span class="section-number-3">11.9</span> 驸马都尉</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-11-9">
<p>
掌驸马。​武帝初置，秩比二千石。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org24aba2c" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org24aba2c"><span class="section-number-2">12</span> 中朝官（内朝官）</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-12">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgb3a4608" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgb3a4608"><span class="section-number-3">12.1</span> 侍中</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-12-1">
<p>
得入禁中。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org6a0f983" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org6a0f983"><span class="section-number-3">12.2</span> 左右曹诸吏</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-12-2">
<p>
诸曹受尚书事，诸吏得举法。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org4e22efd" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org4e22efd"><span class="section-number-3">12.3</span> 散骑</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-12-3">
<p>
散骑骑马，并乘舆车，献可替否。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgd79940a" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgd79940a"><span class="section-number-3">12.4</span> 中常侍</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-12-4">
<p>
得入禁中。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org693f61e" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org693f61e"><span class="section-number-3">12.5</span> 给事中</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-12-5">
<p>
掌顾问应对，位次中常侍。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgc9367d9" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgc9367d9"><span class="section-number-2">13</span> 监御史（刺史、牧）</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-13">
<p>
秦官。​掌监郡。​汉省，丞相遣史刺州，不常置。​武帝元封年初置部刺史，掌奉诏条察州，秩六百石，员十三人。​成帝绥和元年更名牧，秩二千石。哀帝建平二年复为刺史，元寿二年复为牧。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org0a9f5df" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org0a9f5df"><span class="section-number-2">14</span> 郡县</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-14">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orge7113ff" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orge7113ff"><span class="section-number-3">14.1</span> 郡</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-14-1">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org234fa02" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org234fa02"><span class="section-number-4">14.1.1</span> 郡守（太守）</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-14-1-1">
<p>
秦官。​掌治其郡，秩二千石。​有丞，边郡又有长史，掌兵马，秩皆六百石。​景帝中二年更名太守。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgd5d8a32" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgd5d8a32"><span class="section-number-4">14.1.2</span> 郡尉（都尉）</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-14-1-2">
<p>
秦官。​掌佐守典武职甲卒。​秩比二千石。有丞，秩皆六百石。​景帝中二年更名都尉。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org3d6a720" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org3d6a720"><span class="section-number-3">14.2</span> 边郡</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-14-2">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org3d98899" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org3d98899"><span class="section-number-4">14.2.1</span> 关都尉</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-14-2-1">
<p>
秦官。设于扼要之所。​
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgf1b28d4" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgf1b28d4"><span class="section-number-5">14.2.1.1</span> 关长</h5>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org6009097" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org6009097"><span class="section-number-5">14.2.1.2</span> 关尉</h5>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgc28ead2" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="orgc28ead2"><span class="section-number-5">14.2.1.3</span> 关丞</h5>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgec2fb4a" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgec2fb4a"><span class="section-number-4">14.2.2</span> 农都尉</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-14-2-2">
<p>
主屯田植谷。
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org06633ad" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org06633ad"><span class="section-number-4">14.2.3</span> 属国都尉</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-14-2-3">
<p>
安置降附者，掌管属国事务。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org5796960" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org5796960"><span class="section-number-3">14.3</span> 县</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-14-3">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgb1b8513" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgb1b8513"><span class="section-number-4">14.3.1</span> 县令、县长</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-14-3-1">
<p>
皆秦官。​掌治其县。​万户以上为令，秩千石至六百石。减万户为长，秩五百石至三百石。
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org9eefca2" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org9eefca2"><span class="section-number-5">14.3.1.1</span> 长吏</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-14-3-1-1">
</div>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="org8c3b2cc"></a>县丞<br />
<div class="outline-text-6" id="text-14-3-1-1-1">
<p>
秩四百石至二百石。
</p>
</div>
</li>
<li><a id="org4d63b92"></a>县尉<br />
<div class="outline-text-6" id="text-14-3-1-1-2">
<p>
秩四百石至二百石。
</p>
</div>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org5b210c5" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org5b210c5"><span class="section-number-5">14.3.1.2</span> 少吏</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-14-3-1-2">
</div>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="org70511e5"></a>斗食<br />
<div class="outline-text-6" id="text-14-3-1-2-1">
<p>
百石以下
</p>
</div>
</li>
<li><a id="org88c951e"></a>佐史<br /></li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org74f07ec" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org74f07ec"><span class="section-number-4">14.3.2</span> 亭长</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-14-3-2">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org226c33a" class="outline-5">
<h5 id="org226c33a"><span class="section-number-5">14.3.2.1</span> 乡</h5>
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-14-3-2-1">
</div>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="orgd0428f9"></a>三老<br />
<div class="outline-text-6" id="text-14-3-2-1-1">
<p>
三老掌教化。
</p>
</div>
</li>
<li><a id="orgc2562cf"></a>有秩<br /></li>
<li><a id="orgd23c99b"></a>啬夫<br />
<div class="outline-text-6" id="text-14-3-2-1-3">
<p>
啬夫职听论，收赋税。兼为吏民移请过所。手续是由乡到县，经县丞批发。与有秩类似。
</p>
</div>
</li>
<li><a id="orgdba24be"></a>游徼<br />
<div class="outline-text-6" id="text-14-3-2-1-4">
<p>
游徼徼循禁贼盗。
</p>
</div>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org9138526" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org9138526"><span class="section-number-3">14.4</span> 国、邑、道</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-14-4">
<p>
列侯所食县曰国，皇太后、皇后、公主所食曰邑，有蛮夷曰道。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
